{
  "stem": "26359.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Maybe he recognized me from Krasnostav.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I figured Krasnostav is no longer for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went from Krasnostav I was trying to go to Dubno.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The conversion was in [NON-ENGLISH], H-O-R-O-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] A church was still there because of few churches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have churches too many left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when she took me to that church, it was [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is a distance, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few weeks, not more than--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I was the cleaning, the rooms, tidying up, all kind of cleaning work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was recognized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I begged from, the [INAUDIBLE] commander to-- [INAUDIBLE] I don't know what his name was-- the [INAUDIBLE], give me out a certificate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I need to get a rationing, food rationing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you need to have a certificate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then if you'll give me the certificate, I'll be able to get my food rationing without trouble.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he put it on the certificate that he mentioned that Marie Filiniuk is by the Korsze [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he put this name in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That piece of paper helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when I was in [INAUDIBLE], from Korsze I was afraid I was recognized by one of the people from Krasnostav, and I ran away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to Dubno, from Korsze to Dubno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I heard the conversation outside when I was sitting inside, that says, she looks-- the girl, she looks like a Jewish girl more or less.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got cold feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I figured I cannot stay there anymore there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I went with this lady to look for my make believe brother if he's there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went with her.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
